Ya.

62
00:05:20.940 --> 00:05:22.440
Luka goresan di pipinya.

63
00:05:22.440 --> 00:05:25.140
Apa tergores ujung jarum?

64
00:05:25.140 --> 00:05:27.940
Dia pasti kurus, bukan?

